HEADWORD: Pernicketty
<hw>Per*nick"et*ty</hw> }</mhw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Finical or fussy; full of petty
details.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> finical, finicky, fussy, meticulous, painstaking,
persnickety, punctilious.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source> + <source>PJC</source>]</p>

